snippet.title: POP OFF 2 Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Play as a Soda Bottle in a brand new Multiplayer Platformer, "POP OFF 2"!
This vertical platformer will have you rocketing across a beautiful environment as you climb past obstacles, mysteries, secrets and more in this exciting and challenging experience!

Wishlist our game on STEAM: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2562470/POP_OFF_2/?beta=0

Release Date: Oct. 4th

Join our Community!
